{"tid":341826,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"媽媽有病, 資產轉移問題","createTime":"2017-07-31T06:21:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T13:33:16.000Z","uid":124585,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb6ad648967c74b362a0ec1e0bb3884a322b1a31","tid":341826,"uid":124585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:21:15.000Z","msg":"媽媽嚟緊做手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n驚有咩事發生.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢渣X銀行, 有股票喺手. 但係唔想放. 有咩方法可以轉名.<br />\n如果喺渣X銀行開個新Account, 可唔可以就轉到?!<br />\n現金可以提出嚟, 但股票唔知點搞...<br />\n如果可以就咁改個名就最方便......<br />\n同埋個啲股息可以點搞?!<br />\n救連登巴絲解救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9564ae3a35f1a22032fe73ec158f8b060afc0448","tid":341826,"uid":131780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:22:55.000Z","msg":"你媽媽大機會因爲手術要過身? 咩手術黎"},{"pid":"2c76090e9c317e0e0af161ba43f4ff8b89540b56","tid":341826,"uid":49443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:23:23.000Z","msg":"提實貨 去過戶處轉"},{"pid":"49d3ca941e2519da7cbc18556ad0b82363936fce","tid":341826,"uid":124585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:24:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你媽媽大機會因爲手術要過身? 咩手術黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乳癌.....同埋近排個心跳得好快, 可能有另一種隱性病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a426b7db5ba84510bd7e72e50b2051016251eea0","tid":341826,"uid":22617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:25:27.000Z","msg":"搭單問，如果同呀媽有聯名戶口，入面嘅錢係咪自動轉移畀在生嗰個？"},{"pid":"0f2eae293e2c612107e7989a04a56d86f02fdc60","tid":341826,"uid":124585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T06:25:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>提實貨 去過戶處轉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n銀行會收番攞咗出嚟嘅貨嗎?!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1dce0c5712d43037c1f1928090d7c40f572e446","tid":341826,"uid"